<title>Making a personal website using Nanoc</title>
<updated>2012-06-21T22:00:00Z</updated>
<link href="http://members.home.nl/pragtich/" rel="alternate" />

<link href="http://members.home.nl/pragtich/technology/Nanoc.html" rel="self" />

